== AsciiFlow : WYSIWYG ASCIIArt

"AsciiFlow"
http://www.asciiflow.com
is a drawing tool for producing ASCII art. Currently supports lines and boxes, plus an eraser tool. Looks like the ultimate tool for UML diagrams -- no kidding-_.

Thanks to "Julien Kirch"
http://archiloque.net
who reported this to me first.